41
00:03:38,860 --> 00:03:39,600
Yes.

42
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:40,800
Go see them now.

43
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,750
I'll go then.

44
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:42,360
Go.

45
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:01,070
[Fang's Tailor Shop]

46
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,800
Just a moment,

47
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,070
I'll be right there.

48
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,680
Mom.

49
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:37,000
My girl, why are you back from
the provincial capital?

50
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,070
I got transferred back.

51
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,620
When did you come back?

52
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,430
I've been back for a few days.

53
