79
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,560
Listen.

80
00:05:27,630 --> 00:05:29,360
Your father made you several new outfits.

81
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,310
They're really beautiful.

82
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:31,800
They're upstairs. Go try one on.

83
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,270
