98
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:55,330
It's great. Your skills are the best.

99
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,240
Then try it on.

100
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,040
Let me see.

101
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,630
Isn't there an event at school today?

102
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:03,740
Wear this one.

103
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,950
Class Monitor.

104
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:07,950
The dress you wear when you
hosted the event is so beautiful.

105
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:08,870
Yes, indeed, it's really beautiful.

106
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:09,730
Fang Lingyuan.

107
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:13,190
