116
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:48,870
Especially Fang Lingyuan.

117
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,950
The full score is 150.

118
00:07:51,070 --> 00:07:52,950
She got a score of 128.

119
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,480
As the class monitor,
I feel ashamed.

120
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,930
I only got

121
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,270
a score of 120.

122
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,640
My score is 8 fewer than hers.

123
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,810
I'll learn from you.

124
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,240
Let's give her a round of applause.

125
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,630
Congratulations to her.

126
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:08,920
Her score is even higher than our class monitor's.

127
