if you keep staring at me.

136
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:28,560
Come on.

137
00:08:28,630 --> 00:08:30,950
To classmates and friendship, cheers!

138
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,320
Cheers!

139
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,080
