Come on.

142
00:08:35,850 --> 00:08:36,770
Drink up!

143
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,480
Good.

144
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:40,600
You're that...

145
00:08:44,750 --> 00:08:45,510
Fang...

146
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:46,750
Fang Lingyuan.

147
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,270
Can't you recognize your old classmate?

148
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:50,480
Fang Lingyuan

149
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,390
