150
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,960
She's the pride of our class.

151
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,810
I'll punish myself with a drink.

152
00:08:54,810 --> 00:08:56,610
-Lingyuan is amazing.
-Cheers.

153
