Lingyuan.

154
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,860
My son is starting school next semester.

155
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,510
I want to send him to a school
in the provincial capital.

156
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:07,600
I wonder if you know

157
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,740
