Eat!

165
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,670
Haven't you eaten today?

166
00:09:25,550 --> 00:09:27,600
Come on, drink up! Fill it up!

167
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:29,980
Have another cup.

168
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:33,550
Let me tell you,
we had no choice back then.

169
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:35,480
Do you dare to ask questions again?

170
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:37,960
Stop hitting her!

171
00:09:38,030 --> 00:09:39,630
If she tells on us to the teacher,

172
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,760
