173
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:42,770
You dare tell on us to the teacher?

174
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:45,120
If you dare to tell me on the teacher,
I'll kill you.

175
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,030
How dare you!

176
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,610
How dare you!

177
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:49,120
Who do you think you are?

178
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,000
Back then, Jiang Ting

179
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,600
was the teacher's favorite.

180
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:55,510
She was the ringleader in bullying others.

181
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:56,320
Lingyuan.

182
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:57,360
We all

183
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:58,960
used to say behind her back

184
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:01,160
that she was the teacher's running dog.

185
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,030
It's said she killed

186
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:05,030
Zhang Yuan who graduated a year before us.

187
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:06,080
I heard that too.

188
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:12,790
