193
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:20,800
I wouldn't have been so nice to her.

194
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,480
Just now,

195
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,010
how could you even say that?

196
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:27,560
What have you ever done to help her?

197
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,790
I remember when we bullied her back then,

198
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:32,870
you contributed the most.

199
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,450
Not me.

200
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:37,120
Fang Lingyuan got a poker face.

201
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,650
I really want to ignore her.

202
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:40,840
Let me tell you,

203
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,270
Fang Lingyuan...

204
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:45,390
What's new about Fang Lingyuan?

205
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:50,610
This is so awkward.

206
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:02,450
Come on, everyone, have another drink.

207
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,030
