271
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,240
Almost ten years ago.

272
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:33,150
I couldn't find a job after I
got released from prison.

273
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:35,630
Then I became an apprentice
of my current master.

274
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:37,480
I moved here with him.

275
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:40,440
Ten years ago?

276
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,390
Ten years ago,

277
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:46,410
I was about to graduate from university.

278
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,100
Busy with the bar exam?

279
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:50,520
I graduated a year ahead of you.

280
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:53,390
I remember a question
on that year's exam.

281
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:55,630
Facts 3.

282
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:59,220
After Person A and Person B
committed burglary and murder,

283
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,550
they assaulted the police and ran away.

