354
00:18:17,070 --> 00:18:20,000
I was very interested in law
when I was in high school.

355
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:21,550
Actually, before I graduated
from high school,

356
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:23,440
I got the recommendation

357
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:26,130
and was admitted to your university.

358
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:27,830
Li Mufeng.

359
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:29,110
Your package.

