00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:43,480
So

437
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:46,550
many people came to appeal against
the decisions of the cases

438
00:22:46,550 --> 00:22:48,210
that used to be handled by him.

439
00:22:48,750 --> 00:22:49,790
Among them,

440
00:22:50,070 --> 00:22:52,680
there is the criminal of Case 6.28,

441
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,590
Li Mufeng.

442
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,680
The case from 14 years ago

443
00:22:55,890 --> 00:22:57,960
happened in the library next to
the school.

444
00:22:57,960 --> 00:22:59,220
It caused a sensation.

445
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,840
I believe you still remember that case.

446
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:04,270
Li Mufeng insists that

447
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:06,200
Duan Hongshan have made a mistake.

448
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,200
So,

449
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:10,000
I asked you to come

450
00:23:11,590 --> 00:23:13,320
