451
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:15,480
Let's discuss what we should do.

452
00:23:18,110 --> 00:23:20,380
I suggest holding a public hearing.

453
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,240
We can take this opportunity

454
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:22,970
