458
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:31,270
This case...

459
00:23:31,270 --> 00:23:32,550
I agree to hold a public hearing.

460
00:23:32,550 --> 00:23:33,440
We can take this opportunity

461
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:34,700
to check the old cases.

462
00:23:35,030 --> 00:23:37,960
How can a hearing be held so easily?

463
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,840
The case is from 14 years ago.

464
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:41,830
The criminal has long finished serving
his sentence.

465
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:43,550
It's been so many years.

466
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:46,200
Is the conclusion of the case not clear

467
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:48,590
