486
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,240
The person may have got a wrong verdict.

487
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:18,510
And he spent so many years in prison.

488
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:20,170
Isn't this a waste of his time?

489
00:24:29,070 --> 00:24:30,070
Prosecutor Gong.

