00:24:32,310 --> 00:24:32,920
Please.

492
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:37,590
I think

493
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:40,310
we must hold a public hearing

494
00:24:40,310 --> 00:24:41,310
for the Case 6.28.

